snippet.title: Guardian of the Gears - Trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the official trailer for our game, Guardian of the Gears.

Guardian of the Gears is a 3D puzzle adventure game where you navigate and control an interactive environment in order to breathe life back into a decaying world.

Copyright (C) 2017 DigiPen Institute of Technology

Guardian of the Gears is currently in development by DigiPen team Studio76.

We are using Unreal Engine 4 and are a team of 2 designers, 2 programmers, 5 artists, 1 sound designer, and 1 producer.
